Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Prologue}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.00,0:02:24.04,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.99,0:08:32.03,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.68,0:00:04.27,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,There's no way he would like someone like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:08.36,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Why are you assuming you've lost?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:11.02,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You've already lost in spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.02,0:00:13.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's Ichika I'm up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.64,0:00:17.13,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,She's cute and social,\Nand she's popular with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.13,0:00:19.56,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And she has the strength to \Nbelieve in her own dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.90,0:00:22.66,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,If I were a guy, I would choose her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.29,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Besides, there's you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:28.09,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Gee, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.09,0:00:31.55,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Not that I didn't already know that I'm cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:37.08,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,That just makes him even more messed up\Nfor not immediately going out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:39.56,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,How much courage does he think it took me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.83,0:00:41.77,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You confessed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.77,0:00:44.06,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You're amazing, Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.42,0:00:46.91,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,So you haven't yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:50.04,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,He'll never get it through his \Nthick skull unless you tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.04,0:00:51.32,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.88,0:00:54.22,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I said I'd do it if I scored\Nthe highest on our exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.22,0:00:56.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Or if I could bake good bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.30,0:00:59.50,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I kept making up excuses to put it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:02.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's not Ichika's fault or anyone else's.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.44,0:01:03.54,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I did this to myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.80,0:01:05.16,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Okay, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:08.00,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Go ahead and stay cooped up\Nlike this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.00,0:01:09.54,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Always moping like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:12.60,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You and I really are on completely\Ndifferent wavelengths.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:17.80,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,But still, I thought you were a rival.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:22.17,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're no match for me? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.17,0:01:24.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You said we're rivals in love, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.15,0:01:27.07,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You had no trouble admitting that I'm cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.07,0:01:29.93,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Seriously, think about it carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.93,0:01:31.19,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We're quintuplets.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.71,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You're obviously cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.59,0:01:38.83,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Wait, don't you think \Nthis is a bit too short?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.83,0:01:40.68,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:43.78,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I know, but I've never \Ncut it this short before.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:45.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:46.08,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You look cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.08,0:01:48.30,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Y-You'd better be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.30,0:01:49.83,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:51.15,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.47,0:01:55.80,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Nino, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:58.95,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,H-Hey, where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:00.64,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Just come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:02.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What's gotten into you,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:03.31,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Miku?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.91,0:02:06.35,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,There's something I want \Nto talk to you about.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.85,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I want you to hear Miku out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:12.82,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,So long as Futaro{**-kun} knows \Nthat Miku likes him,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.82,0:02:14.86,Italics,,0,0,0,,my lie doesn't make any sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.75,0:02:17.61,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm going to use everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:20.49,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,This is the only way I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.14,0:02:23.11,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,It's the only way I can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.76,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Where are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.76,0:02:30.46,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You've been here before, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.66,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.66,0:02:33.51,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,When I was in elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:35.26,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,When you were in elementary school?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:38.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I still remember that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.10,0:02:45.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That day, I wandered around this area \Nwith Rena, wherever she wanted to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.16,0:02:49.25,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,There's no way I wouldn't have \Nenjoyed traveling with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.25,0:02:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,after she said she needed me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.63,0:02:55.15,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, the sun set, \Nand it was night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.56,0:02:57.40,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,And then what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.23,0:03:01.11,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,My teacher from school was \Nsupposed to come pick me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.81,0:03:05.16,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I got to wait in an empty room \Nat the hotel Rena was staying at.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.56,0:03:07.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I think we played cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.97,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Now it's just a nice memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:12.21,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Was she...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.21,0:03:12.88,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are we done?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.38,0:03:18.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I only figured I'd tell you because \Nyou might be plotting something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.38,0:03:19.88,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But I'm tired of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:24.01,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm done playing your little game, Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.58,0:03:25.43,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.14,0:03:27.27,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.23,0:03:30.77,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,See, I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.24,0:03:32.68,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:37.90,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's safe to assume you were the Miku that \NI met in the school hallway the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.78,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Th-That wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.78,0:03:41.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why did you lie to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.18,0:03:50.28,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You must have figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.44,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,That girl from six years ago was one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.73,0:03:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.30,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,It was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.75,0:03:58.77,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,That was me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.07,0:04:00.29,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.59,0:04:03.69,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,We met six years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:06.36,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.06,0:04:08.18,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:14.45,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Do you remember which good luck charm \Nwe bought together six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:18.07,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Yeah, I still have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:19.82,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'd never forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.37,0:04:22.41,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You're lying, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:24.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.58,0:04:26.45,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I can't trust you right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:28.93,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's go back before we catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:35.83,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Man, didn't the weather forecast \Nsay it was going to be clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.31,0:04:38.62,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Uesugi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:40.09,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Oh, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.38,0:04:42.89,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,You were lost, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.89,0:04:44.86,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Also, what's the plan tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.70,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,The shower's free now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.35,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry for taking it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.28,0:04:54.34,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,My underwear's soaked, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.35,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Y-You can go next, then, Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:57.97,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.55,0:05:00.61,Italics,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm glad I didn't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.19,0:05:07.87,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Wow, Itsuki{**-chan}.\NYou're really going all-in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.87,0:05:08.66,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Not gonna wear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:10.39,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,N-No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.39,0:05:13.11,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm going to throw it out \Nsince it's too much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.11,0:05:14.50,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Ichika,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.11,0:05:17.25,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,don't you have something to say to Miku?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.62,0:05:23.76,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.07,0:05:27.25,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.90,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you all here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.15,0:05:31.50,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Message for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.50,0:05:34.52,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,We're assembling in the main hall\Nin thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:36.32,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Why are {\i1}you{\i0} delivering this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:38.31,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I {\i1}am{\i0} a class rep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:47.58,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,W-Washroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.99,0:05:52.17,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you still fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.17,0:05:53.48,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Tell me what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:55.04,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,No, we're, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:57.55,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Man, that was refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.97,0:06:02.15,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I-It's not a big deal, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.15,0:06:04.13,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is just another day for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:06.50,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,O-Obviously, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.50,0:06:07.85,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,All right, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.34,0:06:10.20,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Anyway, thirty minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:13.06,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Apparently, we're deciding on our \Nelective itinerary for tomorrow, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.12,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Give it some thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.46,0:06:18.44,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry for talking out of turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:19.56,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.07,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Making Fu{**-kun} worry is the last thing I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.24,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,And you need to stop running away like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.24,0:06:26.55,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.97,0:06:31.71,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Miku, you can't keep this up forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.00,0:06:34.08,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Guys, let's make things clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.76,0:06:39.29,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,All of us are looking for a chance \Nto be alone with Futaro{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:42.58,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,That's what I've been saying this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.58,0:06:44.30,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You too, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:46.76,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I can't deny it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.06,0:06:50.57,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,None of us are going to get what \Nwe want if we keep this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:53.30,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm sure that's not anyone's wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:56.00,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Look who's talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:57.43,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You hear me out too, Yotsuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.45,0:07:00.30,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,He's not here anymore, is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.30,0:07:04.44,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,We have elective field trips on our last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.75,0:07:07.69,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,We're choosing from one of five courses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:12.08,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why don't we each choose one of the five?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.37,0:07:13.66,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,The only person who gets a chance
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.66,0:07:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,is the one who happens to be on \Nthe same course as Futaro{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.15,0:07:18.58,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Let's leave it all to luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.58,0:07:19.91,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Agreed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.72,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,There won't be any hard feelings that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.16,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:25.94,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Are really we really gonna do this\Nafter all that scheming?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.94,0:07:27.19,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Are you happy with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:28.72,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,It's only a one in five chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.07,0:07:34.00,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I don't know how to face \NFutaro{**-kun} right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.60,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,So I want my odds to be lower.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.05,0:07:39.80,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I think this is the best option.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.80,0:07:41.73,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,We should have done this from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.89,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Can we just point like usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.89,0:07:46.98,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I bet we'll all choose\Nsomething different anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.27,0:07:49.08,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,One, two...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.45,0:07:56.14,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Yo, Uesugi, which course \Nare we choosing tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.93,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's go for E.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:06.06,Default,Person A,0,0,0,,Course D people, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:08.28,Default,Person B,0,0,0,,What was Course D again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.28,0:08:10.74,Default,Person C,0,0,0,,You know, like, Honnouji Temple \Nand samurai graves and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The historical sites.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.78,Default,Person B,0,0,0,,I don't care about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.78,0:08:16.80,Default,Person C,0,0,0,,You should have checked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:20.30,Default,Person C,0,0,0,,You like Japanese history too,\Nhuh, Ichika{**-san}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.19,0:08:23.10,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I have a tummy ache.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.46,0:08:25.10,Default,Person D,0,0,0,,Course E, over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.52,Default,Person D,0,0,0,,We're leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:39.12,Default,Person E,0,0,0,,Students on Course E, we've arrived \Nat our destination, the Studio Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.44,0:08:42.88,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Actually, I want Course D.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.87,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Miku, can we trade?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.56,0:08:50.38,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Why did she decide she wanted \Nto switch courses with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.77,0:08:54.19,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Ichika was supposed to be the one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:55.89,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.13,0:08:58.88,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,Hey, Nakano{**-san}. We meet again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.84,0:09:03.39,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,She ran away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.39,0:09:04.97,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,She probably hates you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Miku, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.61,0:09:10.41,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.28,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.97,0:09:20.48,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Don't run away, Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.06,0:09:23.90,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Not that I think this is enough\Nto make up for what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.04,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You gotta watch where you're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.66,0:09:30.80,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Nino, I just can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.14,0:09:33.78,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,She's trying to run away again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:34.67,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,What do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:39.93,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Would you like to try on samurai clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.31,0:09:39.93,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,{\an8}Would you like to try on samurai clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:42.58,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Ichika! Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.58,0:09:43.56,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,What about you, Nino?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:48.27,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I just called in sick so I \Ncould keep an eye on those two.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.27,0:09:51.38,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,You aren't here to mess \Nwith her again, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.38,0:09:52.44,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,N-No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.44,0:09:54.77,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I bailed with a stomachache, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.09,0:09:58.07,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I don't expect you to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.19,0:10:01.83,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Even if I can't be forgiven for what I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.26,0:10:07.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to make things right as much as \NI can before the end of the last day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:13.34,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I can't believe you're also here \Nto support Miku, Itsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.59,0:10:14.74,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Yotsuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.74,0:10:19.14,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Are you sure you don't want to tell him \Nthat you were the girl he met six years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:22.95,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,There's no reason to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.95,0:10:25.37,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,As long as I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.37,0:10:26.10,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.13,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Ichika and Nino are here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.24,0:10:31.14,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,You two came, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.14,0:10:34.73,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I guess we're all here on Course E.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.09,0:10:36.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Sheesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.41,0:10:38.99,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Nobody's playing by the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:45.64,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Those two guys are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:47.92,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'll go deal with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.92,0:10:52.00,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Ichika, try to get Miku to wear\Nthe samurai clothes while she's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:54.13,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,G-Get her? How?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.13,0:10:57.76,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Hey, you're great at\Nimpersonating Miku, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.33,0:11:00.64,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You're so mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:04.39,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:08.68,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,May I try on the samurai clothes, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:13.29,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Maeda and Takeda are late as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:16.79,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,And Miku said she'd wait, but she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:19.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I guess she left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.38,0:11:23.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Considering what happened on\Nthe first day, I can't blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.57,0:11:26.83,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.13,0:11:29.93,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,So you did get dressed, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.93,0:11:34.84,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I wasn't planning to, but the staff \Nwere weirdly enthusiastic about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.46,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I don't look weird, do I?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.34,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Y-You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:42.59,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Wh-Where are your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.59,0:11:45.08,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Th-They're taking forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.08,0:11:47.35,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I don't know what to do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.44,0:11:52.13,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Uesugi{**-kun}! Are you really here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.36,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Lured them in good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.88,0:11:58.23,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Looks like Ichika managed to do her part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:00.36,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.41,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,They look good together.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.13,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Futaro!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.51,0:12:20.38,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Take a picture! It's going to go back down!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:22.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,All right. Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.68,0:12:30.77,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Don't go thinking I'm giving you to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.53,0:12:39.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,S... Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.89,0:12:43.91,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.91,0:12:45.89,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,She's drenched.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:47.83,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Like we were yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.83,0:12:50.38,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,What is she going to do \Nabout her underwear?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.67,0:12:53.79,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You told me to watch where I was going.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.79,0:12:56.54,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You should pay attention \Nto your surroundings, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.54,0:12:58.55,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I told you, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:13:01.56,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'll apologize to the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.46,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You should get changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.30,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.35,0:13:07.89,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Before we knew it,\Nwe were talking like normal again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.89,0:13:10.12,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,It's strange, given everything that happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:14.25,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,It's like I stop worrying about silly things\Nwhen I'm with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:19.57,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Like the fact that I'm soaked \Nall the way down to my underwear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.58,0:13:25.57,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,This paper bag is from an underwear shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.96,0:13:27.06,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.06,0:13:28.83,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,Maybe it was the staff.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.13,0:13:31.08,Italics,Miku,0,0,0,,I'll take them up on their offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.78,0:13:41.93,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Good thing you had that underwear, Itsuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.93,0:13:43.05,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:46.05,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I thought I might need it in an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:48.64,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Those guys are still gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.08,0:13:50.78,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.53,0:13:53.69,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Miku?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:56.14,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I-I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.15,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Let's sit down for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:13:59.99,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.26,0:14:02.04,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.30,0:14:03.92,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,How are they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.92,0:14:06.75,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I think things are going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.10,0:14:11.90,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,What do we do now, Yotsuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.22,0:14:16.50,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I picked up Miku's bread, \Nbut I left it back at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:18.52,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,What? B-Bread?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.09,0:14:20.04,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.66,0:14:23.30,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I just need to hand this to Miku, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.64,0:14:27.48,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,The last three days went by so quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:28.39,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.74,0:14:31.30,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Although it was just two days for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.78,0:14:33.43,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,But it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.94,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I got to spend the last day with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:37.17,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,That's good enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:38.19,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Miku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.53,0:14:39.61,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.74,0:14:43.32,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Why is my bread here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.34,0:14:46.15,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You baked that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.61,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I did, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.61,0:14:49.87,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm hungry. I'm going to take one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:52.08,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,That's already...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.24,0:14:58.83,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yum.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:02.55,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I seem to have a bad palate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.55,0:15:06.84,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm not confident I \Ncan give you good feedback,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.91,0:15:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but I can, at least, appreciate your effort.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:13.07,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You must've worked so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.83,0:15:21.35,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:26.61,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I worked really hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.24,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I handed it to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.42,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.42,0:15:36.27,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I think I've been rooting for \Nthe passive one the most
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.27,0:15:40.12,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,because I wanted everyone to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.55,0:15:45.46,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,So I never realized how \Nyou were really feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.46,0:15:47.13,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,So, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.06,0:15:52.26,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I keep getting apologized to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.35,0:15:56.65,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm the one who needs to apologize the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:59.95,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,My mom used to bake for me a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.22,0:16:01.70,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,When I was six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.63,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,She baked bread every day until she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.47,0:16:07.26,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I was reminded of that for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.40,0:16:10.03,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Your mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.37,0:16:14.96,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It was the kind of popular handmade bread \Nthat they serve at small cafés and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.64,0:16:17.65,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,My dad and I loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.96,0:16:21.22,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Anyway, no point talking about me right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.22,0:16:22.04,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.96,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I want you to tell me more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:28.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I never knew any of this, even though \Nwe've spent so much time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:31.80,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I've been so busy thinking about myself,\NI didn't even try to learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.55,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I want to learn more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:35.46,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Everything about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.46,0:16:40.06,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And I want you to know \Neverything about me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.25,0:16:41.81,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.45,0:16:46.59,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,That spot's famous for being used as a \Nmagistrate's office in period dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.59,0:16:49.07,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm content just having\Nbeen able to see it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:52.45,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I'm sure you are. I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.84,0:16:55.70,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I love that big bridge we just crossed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.70,0:16:57.05,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,TV shows again?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.05,0:16:57.83,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.20,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Oh, and I love that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.71,0:17:01.96,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And I love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.35,0:17:03.59,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I love this, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.96,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,That's way too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.33,0:17:06.50,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Not that I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.62,0:17:14.64,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.73,0:17:20.81,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.09,0:17:22.86,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I kept getting in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:27.61,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun}, I'm sorry I kept lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.14,0:17:30.48,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,But what I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.48,0:17:34.63,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I met this really interesting boy today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.63,0:17:37.74,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,And we bought all these \Ngood luck charms together.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.74,0:17:40.85,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,He's still in the main hall right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:42.12,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.50,0:17:44.04,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,You came.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:46.40,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I was bored, being all by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:47.38,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Let's play something.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:50.99,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,H-How about Sevens?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:55.41,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,It was just for a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.79,0:18:00.27,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,But I'm sure I fell in love with you\Nbecause of that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.41,0:18:05.31,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun}, you might \Nnot believe me anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.24,0:18:07.48,Italics,,0,0,0,,but that moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.88,0:18:12.82,Italics,Ichika,0,0,0,,That memory isn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.73,0:18:16.07,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Ichika, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:21.22,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,When I saw them together, \NI couldn't keep my cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.22,0:18:23.33,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Before I knew it, I'd jumped on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.71,0:18:24.54,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.81,0:18:27.33,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I kind of get how you feel now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.77,0:18:31.84,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,If things had happened\Nat slightly different times,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.84,0:18:34.30,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,our roles might've been reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:39.09,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for being so condescending.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.75,0:18:41.14,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:43.35,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,That's not true at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:44.94,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.33,0:18:49.00,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,But at the same time, \NI realized how stupid I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.98,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,You must have, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.10,0:18:56.39,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Miku refused to hold anything\Nagainst you the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.34,0:19:04.24,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Going behind each other's backs, \Ndragging each other down...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.11,0:19:07.54,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,We aren't getting anything \Nout of fighting each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.03,0:19:12.25,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,We aren't enemies, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.79,0:19:14.62,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Let's go apologize to Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.06,0:19:17.45,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,I'm sure we can be on even \Nbetter terms than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.03,0:19:22.68,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,We get to talk about something \Nwe all like, for once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:24.72,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And I love you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.42,0:19:26.02,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.90,0:19:27.77,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.99,0:19:30.84,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.84,0:19:31.52,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.97,0:19:36.02,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I really do love my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:41.24,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Why are you here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.24,0:19:43.25,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You noticed, Miku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.25,0:19:44.89,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,When?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.89,0:19:46.04,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:50.87,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I thought something was up since \NI heard Ichika and Nino's voices.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.54,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Wait, let me walk through this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.87,0:19:55.80,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Which means that "I love you" just now...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.24,0:19:59.28,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It was directed at my sisters hiding in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:02.05,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Did you think...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.69,0:20:04.30,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I was talking about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:08.81,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Y-You're just messing with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.46,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,Are you sure about that, Miku?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:14.08,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,You'd finally managed to tell him\Nhow you feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.40,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.40,0:20:17.44,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I'm not like a certain someone
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,who's stupid enough to go charging in \Nwhen I don't even stand a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:21.96,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Who are you calling stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.96,0:20:26.62,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Besides, Futaro's not as dense as we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.01,0:20:29.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I should have known.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.49,0:20:33.42,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,So, Yotsuba, thanks for the bread.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.43,0:20:37.05,Default,Yotsuba,0,0,0,,I was worried for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:41.54,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Also, I think these are yours, right, Itsuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.54,0:20:42.66,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.66,0:20:43.72,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.01,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Nino.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:47.60,Default,Nino,0,0,0,,Don't bother. We're family.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.97,0:20:48.90,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.90,0:20:50.07,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.07,0:20:51.28,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,And Ichi—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.48,0:20:54.62,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:56.44,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Miku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:58.18,Default,Itsuki,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.11,0:21:03.15,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.99,0:21:07.39,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,I guess falling in love is painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.52,0:21:11.00,Default,Miku,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ichika.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.21,0:21:20.76,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,What they did and talked about from\N then until it was time to meet up again
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.76,0:21:23.80,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,is something only they would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.74,0:21:31.15,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Futaro{**-kun}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:35.26,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I caused you trouble, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:36.73,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.19,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.82,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I went too far yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.18,0:21:43.99,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I didn't even listen to what you had to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:46.09,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.99,0:21:51.46,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,That's exactly right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.87,0:21:54.68,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,You're the worst, \Nglaring at a girl like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.68,0:21:55.64,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.64,0:21:58.15,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I was so sad, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.15,0:21:59.00,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.56,0:22:00.81,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.51,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,It's all a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.01,0:22:08.30,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,All?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.98,0:22:09.99,Default,Ichika,0,0,0,,All of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.90,0:22:19.95,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,Did you hear, Uesugi{**-kun}?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.95,0:22:21.80,Default,Takeda,0,0,0,,About that sneak photographer.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.80,0:22:23.72,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,Sorry, I screwed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.72,0:22:25.11,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,So it {\i1}was{\i0} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:27.99,Default,Maeda,0,0,0,,I tried too hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.17,0:22:31.24,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.60,0:22:33.62,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,I was the one who asked you, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.22,0:22:39.75,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Okay, say cheese.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.70,0:22:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you take the groom to be your wedded\Nhusband, to have and to hold from this day on,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,for better for worse, for richer for poorer,\Nin sickness and in health,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.86,0:23:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to love, cherish, and to obey,\Ntill death do you part?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.49,0:23:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You may now kiss the bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.51,0:23:20.25,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,Now I shouldn't have to worry about \Nbeing fooled by them anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.41,0:23:23.25,Default,Futaro,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.16,0:23:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, seriously, what the...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:36.24,Italics,,0,0,0,,That was the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:40.40,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,That must have been the day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.45,0:23:44.61,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,that I started to feel she was special.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.78,0:23:47.36,Italics,Futaro,0,0,0,,From that moment.
